# Optional — enables AI document generation (Tailored CV, cover letter, etc.).
# The app works fully WITHOUT this: you can write and edit documents by hand.
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and paste your key:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# ⚠️ Vite inlines VITE_* vars into the built JS, so this key is visible in the
# client bundle. Fine for a local, personal tool — do NOT deploy publicly with a
# real key. Get a key at https://console.anthropic.com/
VITE_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
